` when it hears `<term>`.\r\n\r\n```\r\nhubot react \"<term>\" <response>\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Ignore\r\n\r\nTell hubot to forget the last `<term>` `<response>` pair that was uttered.\r\n\r\n```\r\nhubot ignore that\r\n```\r\n\r\n","maintainers":[{"name":"lvh","email":"ncrewforum@gmail.com"}],"time":{"modified":"2016-08-08T19:01:33.236Z","created":"2016-08-08T18:56:19.666Z","4.2.0":"2016-08-08T18:56:19.666Z","4.2.1":"2016-08-08T19:01:33.236Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/lucasvanhalst/hubot-react#readme","keywords":["hubot"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"git://github.com/lucasvanhalst/hubot-react.git"},"author":{"name":"Ben Robbins","email":"ben.robbins@gmail.com","url":"https://b3nj4m.com/"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/b3nj4m/hubot-react/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"README.md"}
